Ranger Help for: nature lore
=============================

SYNTAX:      lore [target]
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   NA
BASE SP:     10
SKILL TYPE:  survival

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to identify creatures, plants, and terrain
features using their knowledge of the natural world. When used on a
creature, it reveals information about the creature's type, habitat,
and notable traits. When used without a target, it provides information
about the current terrain and its properties. The detail of information
revealed depends on the Ranger's experience and skill level.
